\emph on 
differences
\emph default 
 between two points in the incoming wavefront.
 So the 
\emph on 
interferometric phase
\emph default 
 error will be proportional of the 
\emph on 
differential
\emph default 
 TEC 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta T(\Delta x)$
\end_inset 

 between the positions 
\begin_inset Formula $(x)$
\end_inset 

