\layout Standard


\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
L=\lambda\frac{\phi}{2\pi}\approx-4\lambda^{2}T\quad m\label{eq: TEC2meter}\end{equation}

\end_inset 


\layout Standard

So, a TEC of one TECU corresponds to a delay of -64 m @ 75 MHz, or -16 cm
 @ 1400 MHz.
