Ionospheric amplitude effects
\begin_inset LatexCommand \label{sub:Ionospheric-amplitude-effects}

\end_inset 


\layout Standard

The ionosphere mostly affects the phase, but there are some amplitude effects
 also.
 They tend to become important under conditions that are so bad that it
 is better to stop observing.
 
\layout Itemize


\series bold 
